data.description: This property is a 3 bedroom/2 bath, with an attached 2 car garage, 1994 Manufactured Home affixed on a concrete foundation with a crawl space. There is even the potential of a fourth bedroom! Other features included with this home: a large master suite with it's own entrance/exit, two dining areas, tankless/on demand hot water, covered outdoor patio, an oversized two car garage, a corner lot with plenty of RV parking, southern exposure with mountain views, NO HOA or CCRs. The fully fenced yard with full landscaping including a water feature, has been well maintained by the current owners. 2518 N Sharon is a few blocks walking distance to local parks, schools, and Prairie Falls Golf Course. 10-15 minutes to downtown Coeur d'Alene, 35-40 min to the Spokane International Airport.
